Wie zu multiple players (mit Liste):
    - Create List
        - Put all Players in list
        - Query the name of the player
            - check if player is in Liste
                - if yes
                    - nothing
                - if no
                    - add new player to list
                    - create new Div mit namen totaldiv winsdiv lossesdiv
                    - put new dif in statisticsLayout

Wie multiple players (ohne Liste):
    - resetName Button
        - set Name to false
    - If Name == false in submitButton
        - set new name
          - create new div mit namen totaldiv winsdiv lossesdiv
          - put new div in statisticsLayout
    - else
        - nothing